                             [1] - mostly involves keys & mission objects; set 0000FFFF to place all keys in inventory; set FFFF0000 to place all mission objects in inventory; set FFFFFFFF to place both of them
                             [2] - mostly involves later items & BFaW items; set 0000FFFF to place all later items in inventory (but be careful it includes rebirth ending items as well!); set FFFF0000 to place all BFaW items in inventory; set FFFFFFFF to place both of them
