sh2pc.exe+19BBFA0 (01DBBFA0) float - Boat stage time
sh2pc.exe+19BBFA4 (01DBBFA4) float - Boat max speed
sh2pc.exe+19BBFA8 (01DBBFA8) float - Damage points taken
sh2pc.exe+1B7AA2C (01F7AA2C) 2 bytes - Ending Type
sh2pc.exe+1B7AA3A (01f7AA3A) byte - UFO Ending (You have to set ending type to 0 and this ufo memory to 0xFF)
